---
title: Peppercorn Gravy Beef & Veggie Filo Pie with Cheddar Cheese
description: This pie needs to be on a picture-perfect windowsill, with birds singing in the background. The rich beef filling will put that pep back in your step with peppercorn gravy and loveable veggies to add the finishing touch to this pie-perfect scene.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
